Chalmers Beamer Template -- Unofficial community theme
=======================================================

This repository contains an unofficial LaTeX Beamer theme that
approximates the 2026 Chalmers University of Technology visual identity
(the group-wide brand launched in spring 2026).

The theme was built as a community contribution; it is not an official
Chalmers product and has not been reviewed or endorsed by the Chalmers
Communications Department.  For brand-critical materials -- doctoral
theses, licentiate theses, official diplomas, ceremonies, external
publications -- consult the Chalmers Brand Portal and your local
communications officer.


Trademarks and logotypes
------------------------

