Approximations and adjustments
------------------------------

  * The standalone avancez emblem PNGs (`Chalmers-emblem-*.png`) were
    cropped from the official vertical combined logo (`Chalmers-Avancez_
    Comb-vert_*_en.png`) because the Chalmers download portal does not
    publish a standalone emblem PNG.
  * The English wordmark-only PNGs (`Chalmers-wordmark-*.png`) are the
    short Swedish "Chalmers" wordmark file shared between languages.
  * Arial -- the official Chalmers typeface -- is approximated in LaTeX
    by Helvetica via the `helvet` package, since Arial is not a free
    font and Helvetica is the closest Type-1 substitute distributed
    with TeX Live.

If any of the above conflicts with the Chalmers brand guidelines,
please open an issue at
https://github.com/wenlzhang/chalmers-beamer/issues and the asset will
be removed.
